      <title>上诉法院推翻 SEC 对冲基金收费规定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-05/appeals-court-strikes-down-sec-hedge-fund-fee-rule</link>
      <description><![CDATA[位于新奥尔良的美国第五巡回上诉法院推翻了美国证券交易委员会要求对冲基金和私募股权公司向投资者公布季度费用和开支的规定。索纳莉·巴萨克将带来更多报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-05/appeals-court-strikes-down-sec-hedge-fund-fee-rule</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 14:13:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
